    LeftParen
    RightParen
    Percent
    Hash
    Dollar
    Comma

    A
    X
    Y

    Integer
    Identifier

    ADC
    AND
    ASL
    BCC
    BCS
    BEQ
    BIT
    BMI
    BNE
    BPL
